    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a poetic way to put it i guess, but it feels more like... just being invisible. like there's no point in trying to be \"seen\" or anything when the outcome is the same. it's almost peaceful to think about just letting go and not having to fight to be noticed anymore.",
